| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-0365 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 3d8c1ca9-0034-5840-be7c-9e3adcca932f"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
